/* Table: busi_workinfo */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_workinfo (
PackingID int identity,
OP_orderproID int null,
OP_orderID int null,
OP_packID int null,
OP_SKUID int null,
IsPack int null,
OP_shopID int null,
Packingtype int null,
location_no nvarchar(20) null,
depotID int null,
AdminID int null,
Inserttime datetime null,
Packingtime datetime null,
constraint PK_BUSI_WORKINFO primary key (PackingID)
)
go
